{
  "version": "2",
  "title": "Damian's LRv3",
  "author": "Decent",
  "notes": "This profile simulates a Londinium R machines extraction style. This is an advanced profile with some added steps to assist with less than ideal puck prep. Christee-Lee described it as like having a milkshake with extra syrup. Great body and flavour range. 3rd edition. By Damian Brakel",
  "beverage_type": "espresso",
